class Location implements Hashable { 
  num _lat, _lng;
  
  Location([this._lat, this._lng]); 
  
  int hashCode() {
    int result = 17;
    result = 37 * result + _lat.hashCode();
    result = 37 * result + _lng.hashCode();
    return result;
  }
  
  String toString() => "${_lat},${_lng}";
}

void main() {
  var waikiki = new Location(21.271488, -157.822806); 
  var hometown = new Location(48.19366, -122.12681);
  var london = new Location(51.50403, -0.11844);
  var london2 = new Location(51.50403, -0.11844);
  
  HashSet<Location> locations = new HashSet<Location>();
  locations.add(waikiki);
  locations.add(hometown);
  locations.add(london);
  locations.add(london2);
 
  locations.forEach(print);
}
